{"tid":304641,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"秒速5cm 美國版","createTime":"2017-07-01T05:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T11:52:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07582c66354f762b42c06d9f9d96447db8c166b5","tid":304641,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"阿lo多key, 我們還堅信...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 美國路易斯安那州岡薩雷斯一對9歲「小情侶」，因為家庭關係要天各一方，女童高呼「他去了加州，我如何嫁給他？」，兩人分別一刻相擁痛哭，感動不少網民。<br />\n<br />\n梅辛（Merce Meynardie）與邁莉（Mylee）自兩歲時在一個舞蹈班邂逅後，便一直形影不離，梅辛爸爸梅納迪（Glen Meynardie）表示，「我記得他們經常說，兩人是男女朋友關係」。但梅納迪最近在加州找到一份新工作，因此要搬家，「小情侶」被迫分離，梅納迪更稱，「當邁莉獲悉他們要搬，她說『我的一生完了，我還以為會嫁給梅辛，如果他去加州，我如何嫁給他？』」<br />\n<br />\n兩人臨別一刻，他們還穿上情侶裝互相擁抱，難捨難離，令旁人動容，邁莉的姊姊將兩人離別的照片上載到Twitter，「我妹妹的男友要離開，那是最悲傷的道別」，網民都為之感動，希望兩人再有重遇一天，「他們16年後經歷不少可愛及可笑的事情後，20多歲的他們會再相遇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170630/large/1498825957_9aa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498825957_9aa7.jpg&h=14ec9461&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712536efb14d88fe3ae2547cdba85592bde338b9","tid":304641,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"後面個阿媽"},{"pid":"b8c46a3a33ed95cb60adf78a066b50dab68d7a51","tid":304641,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"結局應該都一樣"},{"pid":"158db20b81b3e79ac21c21bcf859bd0e2ce79d63","tid":304641,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"已經見到結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a800985f51a5eb166934d5a3b334feab5b22b35c","tid":304641,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"細路仔點同 毛都未出 轉個撚頭咩都唔會記得"},{"pid":"23c6fc2981c390dd1a63ddf8b6ba5ba8809522c9","tid":304641,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經有bgm喺耳邊響起"},{"pid":"bc9807af70dd5b84aab3f0e19b4430aa630d2893","tid":304641,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:54:00.000Z","msg":"one more time 其實想起了你 我的心會暖"},{"pid":"f2e8f2c9dd99eb13cca998bd38476a2dbebb4b6a","tid":304641,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}